											♫ When I wake up ♫
											♫ in the morning ♫
											♫ I pour the coffee ♫
											♫ I read the paper ♫
											♫ And then I slowly ♫
											♫ and so softly ♫
											♫ do the dishes ♫
											♫ So feed the fishes ♫
											♫ You sing me happy birthday ♫
											♫ Like it&#39;s gonna be ♫
											♫ your last day ♫
											♫ here on Earth ♫
