							</div>
													<div class="Grid Grid--with-gutter d:f@md p-b:4">
								<div class="Grid__cell d:f h:full m-b:.5 m-b:0@md w:12"></div>

								<div class="Grid__cell flx-s:1 p-r:4">
									<p>
											All right. I don&#39;t know if that was necessary to demonstrate —
											(Laughter)
											— but my point is it&#39;s the sound of self-destruction.
									</p>
								</div>
							</div>
